<http://www.semanticweb.org/rajesh.piryani/ontologies/2025/3/SCIMIN_CRM/Granulometry> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                                      rdfs:comment """CQ: Crushing and Milling
What is the particle size and size distribution of the mining waste?""" ,
                                                                                                   """MINNERSA, SGS
In this case, it is the classification of a mineral's size. A particle size analysis determines the proportion of minerals in different fractions. This is an important characteristic when processing minerals.""" .


